ZH: 转录是转换DNA序列为RNA序列的过程。
EN: Transcription is the process of converting DNA sequence into RNA sequence.

ZH: 在生物学中，转录可以发生在细胞核中。
EN: In biology, transcription can occur in the cell nucleus.

ZH: 转录是生物体内信息的重要转移过程。
EN: Transcription is an important process for transferring information within an organism.

ZH: 转录是生物体内基因表达的第一步。
EN: Transcription is the first step of gene expression within an organism.

ZH: 转录过程需要RNA聚合酶的参与。
EN: The transcription process requires the involvement of RNA polymerase.

ZH: 转录后的RNA会被用于合成蛋白质。
EN: The transcribed RNA will be used for protein synthesis.

ZH: 一些转录因子可以加速转录速率。
EN: Some transcription factors can accelerate the transcription rate.

ZH: 转录在生物体内起到了重要的调控作用。
EN: Transcription plays an important regulatory role within an organism.

ZH: 转录包括启动子和终止子的识别。
EN: Transcription includes the recognition of promoters and terminators.

ZH: 转录的产物是具有遗传信息的RNA分子。
EN: The product of transcription is an RNA molecule with genetic information.

ZH: 转录的效率取决于细胞内的调控机制。
EN: The efficiency of transcription depends on the regulatory mechanisms within the cell.

ZH: 在转录过程中，DNA的一部分会被复制为RNA。
EN: During transcription, a part of DNA will be copied into RNA.

ZH: 转录的正确进行对生物体的正常生长发育至关重要。
EN: Proper transcription is crucial for the normal growth and development of an organism.

ZH: 转录在细胞分化和特化中起着关键作用。
EN: Transcription plays a key role in cell differentiation and specialization.

ZH: 转录对于细胞内信号传导的影响至关重要。
EN: Transcription is crucial for the signaling pathways within the cell.

ZH: 转录的失调可能导致疾病的发生。
EN: Disruption of transcription may lead to the occurrence of diseases.

ZH: 转录的研究为治疗疾病提供了新思路。
EN: Research on transcription provides new insights for disease treatment.

ZH: 转录的调控机制在进化过程中发挥了重要作用。
EN: The regulatory mechanisms of transcription play an important role in the process of evolution.

ZH: 转录是生物学研究中的重要课题之一。
EN: Transcription is one of the important topics in biological research.
